**DECISION 2026-05-24:** NOT a separate distribution.

Implementation: add 'karr-foundation' executable to App::karr (script/karr-foundation or bin/karr-foundation, whichever the dist already uses for the main 'karr' bin).

Reasoning: only Perl users will install karr anyway, so a separate dist adds packaging overhead with no audience benefit. Keep it inside App::karr.
